snippet.title: Jelly Express - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Jelly Express on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1945260/Jelly_Express

Jelly Express is a two player co-op physics game. You will be playing two little jellies who will deliver boxes over obstacles to reach their destination. The only tool you have is a wooden board overhead, so use your ability to stretch, jump, and move to keep the boxes steady on the board.

#JellyExpress #trailer #indiegames
